nodes.text: A TIE fighter was in use by the Galactic Empire during the time of the Galactic Civil War. The starship was stationed at a starfighter factory on the Supply moon while it was visited by Darth Vader and the then incumbent Minister of War. As the factory was attacked by forces of the Alliance to Restore the Republic it engaged their fighters but was ultimately destroyed.
This TIE fighter first appeared in Vader - Dark Visions 4 written by Dennis Hallum, with illustrations by Stephen Mooney and colors by Lee Loughridge.
